# Customer Relationship Management (CRM)

This project is a simple and customizable **Customer Relationship Management (CRM)** system built to help businesses manage their interactions with current and potential customers. It includes tools for tracking communications, managing sales pipelines, storing customer data, and improving customer service.

## Features

- Customer database with contact details
- Sales and lead tracking
- Interaction and communication history
- Task and follow-up reminders
- Reporting and analytics dashboard

## Technologies Used

- [Jekyll](https://jekyllrb.com/) (for static site generation)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Ruby / Bundler (for managing dependencies)
- GitHub Pages (for deployment)

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Ruby installed
- Bundler (`gem install bundler`)
- Jekyll (`gem install jekyll`)

